  phaseId: 10
  entries:
  - characterId: 6
    description: The way out is not easy to find. The forest only opens its path
      when the village remembers who it is.
  - characterId: 1
    description: What do you mean?
  - characterId: 6
    description: "There used to be a <b>Resident List</b> in this house. Every villager\u2019s
      name was written on it. But now\u2026 they are disappearing.\n"
  - characterId: 1
    description: You want me to restore the list?
  - characterId: 6
    description: Find the old paper fragments in this house and restore them.
